#

Garlic Herb Pork Tenderloin

40 min
$12.5
220 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyQuickDinnerPork

Description

Juicy pork tenderloin infused with aromatic garlic and fresh herbs, perfect for a satisfying dinner.

Ingredients

  • pork tenderloin: 1 pound
  • garlic cloves: 4, minced
  • fresh rosemary: 1 tablespoon, chopped
  • fresh thyme: 1 tablespoon, chopped
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
